        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1668610369" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15453625583317249806">Purge is a very unsettling read indeed. It tells the story of two women of different generations, against a backdrop of the Soviet occupation of Estonia. Each woman has secrets to hide, and these are slowly revealed over the course of the book. There is a strong undercurrent of violence and fear, though the violence is rarely explicitly described. And there are flies - <i>so many flies</i>. I am not sure what that is all about but read the book and you&apos;ll see what I mean!!</span>
  <span id="freeText15453625583317249806" style="display:none">Purge is a very unsettling read indeed. It tells the story of two women of different generations, against a backdrop of the Soviet occupation of Estonia. Each woman has secrets to hide, and these are slowly revealed over the course of the book. There is a strong undercurrent of violence and fear, though the violence is rarely explicitly described. And there are flies - <i>so many flies</i>. I am not sure what that is all about but read the book and you'll see what I mean!!</span>
  <a data-text-id="15453625583317249806" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
